choices.text:
Facebook, mobile and candies. But for many boys living on the street of a welfare in Kathmandu, action figures and comics do not means anything though. But these disabled kids longing for something to play with. They were very interested, so with some hard efforts from our volunteers from IIT and TU, this made their dream came true. We got a boy to go around with Limelight Nepal in few days ago, to see what the women made them really felt like. #TrekForADream #MakeArtsPartofEducation
Our idea of #womenfriendly is to empower them enough that they can hold their ground when they stand to fight against any social injustice. Night patrolling around women holding torch in their hands #TrekForADream Join us to promote #PeaceandCombatViolenceAgainstWomen #cleanfestival #sonimallegedvictim #freedomfromhunger
Today the women in Kathmandu Durbar square were offered only few cups of tea. They were not asked why they had to go through this social injustice. We left Kathmandu Women's living library Program thinking about the ignore and left out worked by the women in society. Our emphasis on taking the initiative to change this status quo is our main approach to defeat these social injustice and political abuses towards women.
The Women protesting in front of the President's Office. They climbed the building. The women said that they are ready to do anything to bring the killer of sonimal to justice.
